Sentencas: Porous La0.81Sr0.09MnO3 and LSM-YSZ composite electrodes of the solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) were made, and the relationship between the overpotential and the three phase boundary (TPB) length was investigated by constructing a model.
Titulo: The relationship between overpotential and the three phase boundary length

Sentencas: Three-dimensional distribution of TPB for the composite cathode was suggested.
Titulo: The relationship between overpotential and the three phase boundary length

Sentencas: The effective thickness of it was observed to be less than 20 mu m.
Titulo: The relationship between overpotential and the three phase boundary length
